INSERT INTO `Skills` VALUES ('0405820c-f9cc-43b1-a961-baab79c9c980','Create your own star planisphere','If you like to look at the stars, that\'s the tool that you were missing. We only need some cardboard and scissors ;)','Barcelona',6,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1480264801016-9f3227820ca5?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=da2475765089b08c8dbacddd256175d5','2018-07-05 10:38:53','2018-07-05 13:39:42','4cf7d8fa-3814-4a1a-afd6-8051e064d4a9','56c74284-0d07-48ed-9850-5706ae500a25'),('0ad44548-2523-443c-a2f6-bf6904407289','What is a bootcamp? Step in.','JavaScript is simply the best choice to learn coding today. In fact, it’s the only programming language that can run both in the browser and on the server, allowing you to build entire products with one technology. Not even to mention the ability to create hybrid and native mobile apps. I will tell you what a bootcamp is and how it can teach you to become a better developer. ','Barcelona',5,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502758898459-10885c4d334c?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=4e5c129143d0c68ca8fb7d9a22a70845','2018-07-05 11:46:19','2018-07-05 12:21:45','99508130-df5c-41f2-bfce-2ee95f38b756','b2b5e816-d8d6-4347-b152-81bfe341ca90'),('164028a9-15d6-4606-b584-f24310837de1','Manage your Browser Tabs','You need to have some knowledge about: Google Chrome, Opera,  Edge, Internet Explorer, Brave, Safari, Mozilla Firefox, Maxthon, SeaMonkey, Avant.\nThen you will learn how to work with all of them at once with only 2 hands. You will see how all the tabs flow from one browser to another to improve the overall browsing speed.','Barcelona',5,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517400777233-4562ed6ebc63?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=98e3773bde34f188e7a1163a72f1c374','2018-07-05 12:07:38','2018-07-05 13:31:39','ded22b44-465f-4378-a5f1-a3b2f1de454a','b80e7d22-f276-443f-9c3e-5f8f414d891c'),('1ce4c95c-9bc9-4176-9a27-10be5dd3e727','How to be in two places at the same time','Happy to teach my techniques of how you can do a bootcamp while raising two kids below 5 years old!','Barcelona',28,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511762180596-d03b808430fe?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=6538a2a22a0514b3eb29b3f7b85d9475&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=60','2018-07-05 11:03:11','2018-07-05 16:25:30','64916ebd-e419-4821-9a5a-90ec6845b1a0','8ddebf3a-821b-49ed-8962-8985c6f15792'),('2ed2966b-631a-44fe-9e40-1bb820b0c98f','Surf in all the social Networks','How to be present in all the social networks and not becoming insane while accomplishing this almost Mission: Impossible','Barcelona',2,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502868032459-aa78309e3503?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=4b89b05e644429cae9dd049ed152b98c','2018-07-05 11:56:59','2018-07-05 12:34:52','bbcbc9ff-1fcf-4eb4-8078-79e6fe137c65','b80e7d22-f276-443f-9c3e-5f8f414d891c'),('3d67dca6-36df-4e47-b7e3-99578e7c0eaa','How to delegate your work tasks to Fiverr!','There is nothing better than to work as a developer and living la vida loca. What\'s even better, don\'t feel like working? Easily delegate all your tasks on Fiverr, for only 5 dollars they will do the job for you. You still get to harvest the fruit!','Barcelona',17,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1468436139062-f60a71c5c892?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=30fc6508425eeff7d66b9b777f264285','2018-07-05 10:37:24','2018-07-05 15:17:16','ded22b44-465f-4378-a5f1-a3b2f1de454a','761f66df-5c55-4bd3-9496-f71329b667ee'),('3d806aa5-0553-4828-9f82-2c1ab31b8fa7','How to make a dramatic entrance!','Lights, a scene,  music is the mean, to woe the audience into your comb. I\'ll guide you step by step how to master any performance. Got the light, time to pick your fight!','Barcelona',11,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504838986326-0f4d3ce9cf63?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=5fc8eb7df2c29564f15cc201aecca286','2018-07-05 11:02:58','2018-07-05 13:13:40','bbcbc9ff-1fcf-4eb4-8078-79e6fe137c65','d4ed7dc8-87de-42ab-b100-c5e1860f22ef'),('3fa41ac1-e109-4292-9469-23350d90a2b7','Dance samba like a real Brazilian','Interested about this contagious rhythm? Join me and learn the basic steps to look good during carnaval :)','Barcelona',9,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518886849533-2a7b825fe852?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=caafb9f7f5f2804d01e4f7d8ba483418&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=60','2018-07-05 10:54:30','2018-07-05 15:33:39','98d24066-05d8-4e42-9c92-310edfc255c4','8ddebf3a-821b-49ed-8962-8985c6f15792'),('430bbebb-ac21-4d6f-a925-e5c5be12305e','Getting access to any local area network','You have a machine, it has a local ip-address mask. Any time it speaks with a router in the network it expose a mac-address to that network. Don\'t be afraid, i will teach you to break any firewalls and masks that might be blocking you to access a network and the machines in it. Easy as pie.','Barcelona',3,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1527754525882-563050c6618c?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=ae89f3f37636c9a5e94d2e30028850ab','2018-07-05 11:26:05','2018-07-05 13:20:55','abcb42e5-e8d9-4230-b5f6-f5835ce7b402','25b056b0-d0cf-45e0-bde9-7ecbb721d2f5'),('4b02f066-2b22-4f9f-a405-bd86b61d829c','Play golf bare-food','You\'ll receive all the knowledge that I\'ve been gathering after practicing this extreme sport for more than 10 years.','Barcelona',5,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523867386632-d0107d6e79ec?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=68fd3a7c7e6818d62f4af37c2c7957e5','2018-07-05 11:01:04','2018-07-05 13:20:37','64916