in this field, a one-for-all solution, until now! I will share the recipe to this new secret, universal-for-all sauce that matches every dish and every-ones taste! Mol ben!','Barcelona',5,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505576399279-565b52d4ac71?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=6e674fbe3dd51d4fed8ee389f367fcbe','2018-07-05 11:14:20','2018-07-05 12:37:54','cfb0f28a-8741-47d5-ab74-859c665f54ed','e487a817-3089-44f1-bb03-a6a46b6a664d'),('71e82d2e-f619-42d0-acf0-4e97fdac7d27','Teach your dog to be your Wingman','Everyone loves dogs right? Did you know that dogs are the perfect wingmans, they\'ll make the introduction for you. You\'ll notice a 1000% spontaneous increase of social contact when out. Time to make a change in your life. Suit Up! ','Barcelona',18,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520824646108-ead469543c94?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=007fcad23b9611ae11ecf953da4a176e','2018-07-05 11:06:57','2018-07-05 16:24:17','27819d4a-72ba-4fce-aae3-569d2ef0ed3c','d4ed7dc8-87de-42ab-b100-c5e1860f22ef'),('74479ab3-794b-44b4-b3c5-f98ce548d42b','First Steps to conquer a dancefloor','One-two-three, five-six-seven! This is the count you need to keep in mind when entering a sizzling latino dancefloor. The genres and styles all blend, you must never forget that your HIPS DON\'T LIE! We will keep that in mind when listening to various moods such as Salsa, Tango, Bachata, Rumba, Son and more...','Barcelona',7,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504647164485-1d91e1d0a112?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=08547036baebef4d0a4c8854d2f55693','2018-07-05 10:36:04','2018-07-05 14:39:39','98d24066-05d8-4e42-9c92-310edfc255c4','fd6b9367-f918-42d5-b666-c9e46cf95669'),('7dd604ac-b3e4-41e4-a83d-fa3007315add','10 ways you can be more funny!','The magic 10 ways on becoming a more funny person. The secret is don\'t try to hard, just be yourself. I\'ll give you the unique opportunity to learn my 10 ways of being funny.','Barcelona',7,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506903836541-e18b4ba42343?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=63f790c002aea61e8978558f5018b875','2018-07-05 10:47:26','2018-07-05 12:32:04','27819d4a-72ba-4fce-aae3-569d2ef0ed3c','761f66df-5c55-4bd3-9496-f71329b667ee'),('7eeada71-f849-48e8-a48a-249af5d66cbb','Student life-hacks from an expert','You might not know that you can switch around the batteries in your remote-control to preserve power in them. It\'s a hack that i learned when working at a tv-repair shop for a summer. I got tons of these hacks that will turn your bare-scraped student life to the life of a millionaire (well...). I think you get it.','Barcelona',5,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1485436442739-c12c6e3673af?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=95559eda9ad2d2054058cee5f57377d4','2018-07-05 10:59:07','2018-07-05 12:27:40','4cf7d8fa-3814-4a1a-afd6-8051e064d4a9','e487a817-3089-44f1-bb03-a6a46b6a664d'),('8044ea4d-e5a6-4835-a9e0-04faa018c803','Covfefe, make up new words today!','I will teach you to create new awesome words to make America great again. Covfefe!  ','Barcelona',6,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1490029580952-6f9a7da258fb?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=8725b703e50f6e1a0fd374e387917470','2018-07-05 11:27:33','2018-07-05 12:40:28','abcb42e5-e8d9-4230-b5f6-f5835ce7b402','92759eee-5a0f-42a3-a21a-5796543fe69a'),('8a596908-a31b-46e7-a7ff-9102ca4c9b25','North Korea, all you need to know.','All the things you need to know from North Korea. Statistics of all kinds, funny facts and a lot more. You\'ll be considering to become a North Korea citizen after this session.','Barcelona',11,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1495020689067-958852a7765e?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=deb795cd4bf5c713ec53ccb066dbb944','2018-07-05 11:22:57','2018-07-05 13:20:47','99508130-df5c-41f2-bfce-2ee95f38b756','c5aff127-ffbe-4b87-ad80-007cffe99409'),('8c16767d-21b0-42f0-9d24-40f29650c3b8','How to love the new in-laws','So, i went on tinder. Logged in, created a user, chose some fairly recent snaps of my smug face. Now all of a sudden i\'m dating this girl, and you know what, she\'s a keeper! But then what: you need to meet her friends, family and colleagues, and get approved. Recognize this dilemma? Well i have a tiny secret on how to make friends with your mother-in-law-to-be!','Barcelona',11,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520824754996-684c524945b8?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=4b7b3ae44be64996aff390a7304e1a25','2018-07-05 10:48:46','2018-07-05 13:15:05','27819d4a-72ba-4fce-aae3-569d2ef0ed3c','fd6b9367-f918-42d5-b666-c9e46cf95669'),('a11ab11c-b610-4ae9-9daf-15f756afca56','How to be a Picky !%#?*@','Got codeworks presentations incoming? I\'ll teach you how to review  and give proper feedback the presentations.','Barcelona',7,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1485827404703-89b55fcc595e?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=9a2aa0a1b20e2169000e6f136ff87868','2018-07-05 11:40:29','2018-07-05 13:18:13','ded22b44-465f-4378-a5f1-a3b2f1de454a','b2b5e816-d8d6-4347-b152-81bfe341ca90'),('afe16cad-3b20-4540-8fb5-6bd0ad8923d9','Fall asleep anywhere! Anytime.','Resting and sleeping is the honey of our life. But sometimes life gives you lemons. That\'s why, i\'ll teach you the valuable skill of falling asleep anywhere. Is your boss late to the meeting, check! Is your teammate talking too much, check! Don\'t enjoy the senior thesis presentation, check! ','Barcelona',10,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522357262022-50fd510ac901?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=74baf8687052e3550746042e195397a0','2018-07-05 10:42:47','2018-07-05 15:17:59','4bf5bdcf-8905-43b2-8c57-f29a7869e303','761f66df-5c55-4bd3-9496-f71329b667ee'),('b8bfe5c8-68d5-4353-9868-230147233770','How to achieve absolute knowledge','In relative terms, this is not a simple task. It\'s not impossible and should be achievable over two beers and a pack of cigarettes (your treat). The Holy Grail of this quest is known as the Theory of Everything, something i\'ve been reading about lately, i can share some litterature tips too. Cheers!','Barcelona',13,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502852365377-bc7a0bea8e5b?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=7861f987c5f41362a30592addc02d020','2018-07-05 10:28:08','2018-07-05 13:19:53','99508130-df5c-41f2-bfce-2ee95f38b756','fd6b9367-f918-42d5-b666-c9e46cf95669'),('bb2a3eb5-7272-467a-9ff8-bb4fdb1852fb','Instructables for non-millenials','We all know how irritating it\'s to hear \"what does that mean\" when you are sharing ideas with people that don\'t belong to your generation. It\'s a problem and i have the solution. It will eventually become a fortune-500 startup, but for now, while i\'m finishing the elevator pitch, i will share the idea with you (with an instructable, id needed)','Barcelona',13,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1528025445130-97588f3b72e5?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=cd464d4ac7532fae4d2f9eee12e4f21a','2018-07-05 11:04:57','2018-07-05 12:34:49','4cf7d8fa-3814-4a1a-afd6-8051e064d4a9','e487a817-3089-44f1-bb03-a6a46b6a664d'),('c5c729e9-c11f-46d5-ab34-6059cdbc9445','How to build a wall','I will build a great wall -- and nobody builds walls better than me, believe me --and I\'ll build them very inexpensively. I will build a great, great wall on our southern border, and I will make Mexico pay for that wall. Mark my words. I can teach you to become awesome too.','Barcelona',6,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506747111041-18b1844bf60f?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=e88d254df909be115a0b99803ba176ea','2018-07-05 11:23:53','2018-07-05 13:51:14','4cf7d8fa-3814-4a1a-afd6-8051e064d4a9','92759eee-5a0f-42a3-a21a-5796543fe69a'),('ceb1157b-dfc8-4ff6-8b4e-40ceacc3eeea','How to not wear your favorite clothes','Tired of always choosing the same pieces even not having space to storage more articles at your closet? I will be happy to share my technics of how you can actually use every item that you have.','Barcelona',9,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520006403909-838d6b92c22e?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=cd5c81517b22ee13e47484cddb56d16c&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1650&q=80','2018-07-05 11:41:07','2018-07-05 16:24:08','27819d4a-72ba-4fce-aae3-569d2ef0ed3c','8ddebf3a-821b-49ed-8962-8985c6f15792'),('d8cc2231-bd8c-4def-a534-5fb345c04fab','101: How to Sauna like a true Finn','Sweat. Heat. Beer. Tears. Not for the weak! Step into the world of Finish sauna culture.  I\'ll teach you how to heat up and prepare the traditional smoke sauna. The sauna is also accompanied by a dip in the cold and refreshing dip in the lake and rolling in the snow.  ','Barcelona',21,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1463801353705-a4879313362c?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=aeb53d3ae4a70c0d6f01e338419480ae','2018-07-05 10:14:43','2018-07-05 14:43:13','4bf5bdcf-8905-43b2-8c57-f29a7869e303','82f60535-91ae-48be-b5c3-cb8b75b5d39d'),('e3c23d2d-a952-411e-a983-12fc703c1a0b','Sheep herding: How to deal with the black sheep!','I\'ve been a sheep farmer for years, I\'d love to share my experience and passion on the proper herding techniques. Sheep will bring comfort and light into your life, and easy your mind from your daily routines.','Barcelona',9,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518303381723-e97614db478d?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=3f9198817ef0d0eb269226bd39f43217','2018-07-05 10:25:51','2018-07-05 13:33:32','9355c7df-b054-4595-9b5f-5ad47907ed9d','82f60535-91ae-48be-b5c3-cb8b75b5d39d'),('ea6fb1e1-0d48-427a-b7a5-98637ba95513','How to make \'pa amb tomàquet\'','Learn all that you need to prepare this simple but delicious traditional Catalan food.  Anyone can do it with some hints!','Barcelona',8,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1446611720526-39d16597055c?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=ddd325530f6229e9085c37beda65707a','2018-07-05 10:33:33','2018-07-05 14:42:52','cfb0f28a-8741-47d5-ab74-859c665f54ed','56c74284-0d07-48ed-9850-5706ae500a25'),('f5a75e7e-1628-49f0-aaae-c73342d6bed5','Agnosticism gets you nowhere!','Huxley coined this word, with the meaning that knowing or believing something without scientific proof does not actually make it exist. Such as where all the worlds missing keys or odd socks are. Or if there exists god or higher being. I will proof that this doctrine takes you nowhere, and how to avoid needing to prove it scientifically.','Barcelona',2,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1473997094636-80cc50db3e0c?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=098e412c07700eb18744c3a49018f7b3','2018-07-05 11:40:35','2018-07-05 13:21:26','9355c7df-b054-4595-9b5f-5ad47907ed9d','25b056b0-d0cf-45e0-bde9-7ecbb721d2f5'),('f982d1ab-e144-4032-8fc3-3bb6ba5f4632','Teach your pet penguin to fly','I know it can\'t be done, at least in classical childrens litterature, penguins don\'t fly. They just flap around. But if you manage to keep a penguin as a pet (you must live in the southern hemisphere, as there are no penguins on Arctis) i can help you bring it up and teach it the proper techniques to get some air under its flaps.','Barcelona',12,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1449172421446-78de20b4899c?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=7ffbd13861a08481a15181015355f2ef','2018-07-05 11:31:39','2018-07-05 15:17:30','07786342-e144-4b2a-9649-8086801b93e2','25b056b0-d0cf-45e0-bde9-7ecbb721d2f5'),('fa905b9c-4352-4349-8d9a-0c3bd2b038d5','Stop hitting like a ... Lesson in Boxing','Put your hotpants on and let\'s go boxing! I\'ll teach you the basic hits and punches. Let\'s go! Got experience teaching nerds how to fight!','Barcelona',4,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1474224017046-182ece80b263?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=5f76340c270a7e44be3ee54b9f98c2ff','2018-07-05 11:09:58','2018-07-05 13:19:33','6d0b4d81-d276-4eca-900e-e193fd34795d','d4ed7dc8-87de-42ab-b100-c5e1860f22ef'),('fcc688f6-c1ed-4652-8a6e-778895d011ad','Advanced JS, get introduced.','Function.prototype.bind = function(){ \n  var fn = this, args = Array.prototype.slice.call(arguments), object = args.shift(); \n  return function(){ \n    return fn.apply(object, \n      args.concat(Array.prototype.slice.call(arguments))); \n  }; \n};','Barcelona',8,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487673179604-cb1d69e11c1f?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjF9&s=1c2d584be513fb46c954cb7c9519b932','2018-07-05 11:43:32','2018-07-05 13:30:30','bbcbc9ff-1fcf-4eb4-8078-79e6fe137c65','b2b5e816-d8d6-4347-b152-81bfe341ca90'),('fcc7ece9-2dfc-4782-9b7b-91f4e546e077','Wear a wig. Learn to hide your baldness.','I\'m the most successful person ever to run for the presidency, by far. Nobody\'s ever been more successful than me. I\'m the most successful person ever to run. If you want to be like me you need to know how to wear a wing, to impress the ladies.','Barcelona',13,0,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1528398447722-33c404b18fc0?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&q=80